cards.content: Deploy your own cloud instance with dedicated CPU, SSD drives, and RAM – just for your web application or development environment. On the edge, out of the control of centralized parties – the next generation of the Data Center industry.

cards.content: Allows a nearly unlimited amount of storage to be always available, anywhere – with constant backup and snapshots working out-of-box, powered by ThreeFold Grid storage power.
